                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440304-name-467" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440304-name-467" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440304-name-467" type="surname" value="MANN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440304-name-467" type="given" value="ALEXANDER"></interp>ALEXANDER MANN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a salesman. I had several pairs of boots on the 3rd of Feb.—I missed one pair—these are them—the prisoner had been in my shop that day—she came again after that, and I told her I had lost a pair of boots on the 3rd, and that she had pawned them—she said, "How can you say so?"—I said, "I know you have"—she then went down on her knees, and said, "I hope you will forgive me."</p>
               <p>
